rs can choose from a diverse set of avatars to personalize their experience.\n*   **Conversation Window:** A real-time transcript of the conversation will be displayed, allowing users to review the dialogue as it happens.\n*   **Feedback Panel:** This non-intrusive panel will provide real-time feedback on key metrics.\n*   **Controls:** Simple and intuitive controls will allow the user to start, pause, and end the interview.\n\n### **2. The Core Interaction: Seamless Audio and Lifelike Conversation**\n\nThe primary mode of interaction will be voice, creating a natural and immersive mock interview experience.\n\n**Live Audio-to-Audio:**\n\n*   **Technology:** Leveraging advanced speech recognition and text-to-speech technologies, the platform will enable a seamless, low-latency conversation.\n*   **Natural Language Processing (NLP):** The AI will be powered by a sophisticated NLP model, allowing it to understand and respond to the user's answers in a conversational and contextually relevant manner.\n\n**Native Text-to-Speech:** The AI's voice will be generated using a high-quality, native text-to-speech engine, offering a range of natural-sounding voices that users can select from.\n\n### **3. Real-Time Feedback: Your Personal Interview Coach**\n\nTo provide immediate and actionable insights, the platform will offer real-time feedback on various aspects of the user's performance.\n\n**Key Feedback Metrics:**\n\n*   **Fluency and Pace:** A visual indicator will show the user's speaking rate, helping them maintain a clear and steady pace.\n*   **Filler Word Usage:** The system will detect and highlight the use of filler words like \\\"um,\\\" \\\"ah,\\\" and \\\"like,\\\" helping users become more aware of these habits.\n*   **Sentiment Analysis:** The AI will analyze the user's tone and provide feedback on their perceived confidence and enthusiasm.\n*   **Keyword Match:** For technical interviews, the system can track the use of relevant keywords and concepts.\n\n### 